Anna Quayle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anna_Quayle 0 Anne V. M. "Anna" Quayle (born 6 October 1932) is an English former actress. In 1963, she received a Tony Award for Best Featured Actress in a Musical for her performance in the original production of Stop the World – I Want to Get Off.
